- Use Next.js App Router conventions (app/ directory, not pages/)
- Prefer server components unless interactivity is required (then use "use client")
- Use Tailwind utility classes only (no inline styles, no CSS modules)
- All API calls go through /api/* routes (never call Supabase or Claude directly from client components)
- Always import Supabase from lib/supabase.ts
- Use Framer Motion for quiz transitions and animations
- Use next/image for all images with proper alt text
- Always use TypeScript with proper types (no `any`)
- Never hardcode secrets or API keys
